<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #007BFF;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007BFF;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>I WANT TO HIRE YOU!</h1>
        <p>Accept my offer for the case</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear Lawyer,</p>
        <p>I am interested in hiring you for my case. Please review the details below and let me know if you are willing to take on this case:</p>

        <p>If you are interested in representing me, kindly click the button below to accept the offer:</p>
        <a class="button" href="http://localhost:3000/cases">Accept Offer</a>

      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
